=20
with an analytical prose worthy of a barrister? What induced her to swap her=
=20
status as Delhi's most-favoured dinner party guest for night marches and=20
sit-ins at the dam sites, and even, possibly, jail? Why did the whimsical=20
chronicler of "small things" - the beetles and creeping, lush greenery of=20
Kerala - turn to fighting big things such as nuclear bombs, dams, the Indian=
