block. Here, where she writes and spends most of her day, she has none of th=
e=20
small army of servants considered necessary by middle-class Delhi. Her flat=20
is surrounded by the contradictions of Indian development, which she analyse=
s=20
in her essays: a comfortable suburb of New Delhi, where cows rummage in the=20
